\u2019s a simple script to delete log files older than 7 days:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f241a2c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f241a2c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><code>import os<br \/>import time<\/code><\/p><p><code><code><\/code><\/code><\/p><p>log_directory = &#8220;\/var\/logs\/myapp\/&#8221;<br \/>seven_days_ago = time.time() &#8211; (7 * 86400)<\/p><p><code><br \/>\n<\/code><\/p><p><code>for file in os.listdir(log_directory):<br \/>    file_path = os.path.join(log_directory, file)<br \/>    if os.path.isfile(file_path) and os.path.getmtime(file_path) &lt; seven_days_ago:<br \/>        os.remove(file_path)<br \/>        print(f\"Deleted: {file}\")<\/code><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-338b009 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"338b009\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Task for you\ud83d\ude80<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a5f6c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4a5f6c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Modify the script to back up the logs before deleting them.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ecfb51 e-flex e-con-boxed wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no elementor-invisible e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5ecfb51\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1de6d39 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1de6d39\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2.Managing Infrastructure  with Python<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b46b65 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6b46b65\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Python works well with Infrastructure as Code (IaC) tools like <strong>Ansible<\/strong>, <strong>Terraform<\/strong>, and <strong>AWS Boto3<\/strong>. It helps in provisioning, configuring, and managing cloud resources efficiently.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b56ff38 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b56ff38\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Example: Creating an AWS EC2 Instance with Boto3<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62a8f37 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"62a8f37\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: var(--text-align);\">import boto3&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: var(--text-align);\">ec2 = boto3.resource(&#8216;ec2&#8217;)&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p>instance = ec2.create_instances(<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ImageId=&#8217;ami-0abcdef1234567890&#8242;,&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; InstanceType=&#8217;t2.micro&#8217;,<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; MinCount=1,<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; MaxCount=1,&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;print(&#8220;Instance Created: &#8220;, instance[0].id)<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9957409 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9957409\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Task for you\ud83d\ude80<\/h5>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59575b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"59575b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Modify the script to launch an EC2 instance with a specific security group and key pair.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7b9b757 e-flex e-con-boxed wpr-particle-no wpr-jarallax-no wpr-parallax-no wpr-sticky-section-no e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7b9b757\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-